de.ovgu.wdok.guinan.connector.slideshare

Class GuinanSlideshareConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.wdok.guinan.connector.GuinanConnector
      • de.ovgu.wdok.guinan.connector.slideshare.GuinanSlideshareConnector

  • public class GuinanSlideshareConnector
extends GuinanConnector
    GuinanSlideshareConnector is a special connector that forwards queries from the GuinanMaster to the Slideshare API, transforms the XML result from Slideshare into GuinanResults and sends a list of those results back the master
    Version:
    0.6
    Author:
    Katrin Krieger

      • query

        public java.util.ArrayList<GuinanResult> query(java.lang.String query)
        Implementation of query method (overrides (empty) implementation in the superclass).
        The endpoint is set by the @Path annotation. It produces JSON, hence the produced list of GuinanResults will be serialized to JSON.
        Overrides:
        query  in class  GuinanConnector
        Parameters:
        query - the query string, extracted from the URL containing the parameter "q", e.g. "http://localhost:8080/Guinan/slideshareconnector/query?q=foo"
        Returns:
        an ArrayList with GuinanResults containing the response from Slideshare
